Package main.java.com.bdreiss.dataAPI

Class DataModel

java.lang.Object
main.java.com.bdreiss.dataAPI.DataModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class DataModel extends Object implements Serializable
Class that represents a data model for keeping track of ailments.

It contains methods to store and retrieve data for causes, symptoms and remedies relating to ailments. The data model represents dates and intensity (see Intensity) of these fields in a class named Datum.

Author:
Bernd Rei√ü bd_reiss@gmx.at
